Build a single-page lead generation website for a product coffee bucks — define the product, the audience, and the value prop.
MUST-HAVES
* A hero section with a clear headline, sub-headline, and primary CTA
* A lead capture form (Name + Email + CTA button at minimum)
* Form data must be stored — Google Sheets, or anything lightweight works.
* At least one section that builds trust or explains value (features, how it works, social proof — your call)
* A confirmation state shown to the user after successful form submission
